e allowing users to maximize productivity a laptop computer is one of the most versatile tools you can have top laptops like dell toshiba lenovo and hp laptops come with various features dimensions and specifications to fit professional needs portability options keep you productive onthego the more portable a laptop is the easier it is to use in different settings with this in mind brands create models that are thin and lightweight screen size is a significant factor to consider screen dimensions vary often ranging from  inches to more than  inches compare memory and storage options on various models memory and storage specifications determine how quickly a device runs and how much data it can hold laptops use memory to access programs and pull up files many hp asus and dell laptop models have between gb and gb of memory value models often have gb of memory which may be sufficient for basic tasks many of the best laptops have gb which is a good amount for most users some models have expandable memory slots permitting users to upgrade memory as needed storage options limit the need for remote data storage and keep files readily available many models offer between gb and tb of storage space battery life affects laptop functionality laptop computers often have long battery lives due to the reduced power needs of lightweight hardware battery life is particularly important to users who often work in different settings some models offer more than  hours of battery life based on average usage patterns consider your usage habits while comparing battery life specifications gaming video editing and other memoryheavy activities use power more rapidly than internet browsing and word processing what features are important in student laptops mobile workstations are an ideal solution for students they should be as lightweight as possible since they are often transported between classes and buildings users should select a laptop with an operating system that allows access to commonlyused programs at academic institutions an extended battery life helps students go all day without access to a power source are laptops suitable for gaming laptops replicate the functionality and speed of many desktop models many can smoothly handle many popular games and some tolerate heavyduty gaming programs since they balance portability and computing power their graphic and video capabilities differ from the capabilities of desktop computers gaming laptops often have highend video and graphics cards large amounts of memory and fast processors which operating system is optimal for laptops laptops come with several different operating system options models that run on chrome rely on cloud access for programs and files minimizing the computers overall need for storage and memory its ideal for users who have nearconstant access to the internet another option is ios used on apple products the other main option is windows both ios and windows are versatile operating systems that run well on these devices finding the best laptops for your home and business needs is an effective way to get more done in less time research our huge selection of laptops from top brands including hp dell toshiba and lenovo laptops to discover models that accommodate your favorite programs more less hp pavilion ccst  laptop computer th gen intel® core™ i tb sata hd gb ddr win  intel hd graphics  item    model  kuuaaba  add to favorites operating system windows  home processor th generation intel® core™ iu processor display inch diagonal full hd ips brightview wledbacklit  x    each offer details            add to cart hour pick up price  instant savings   each astprice after savings dell igry  laptop computer intel i gb ssd gb ddr win  intel® hd graphics  item    model  igry  add to favorites inch hd  x  truelife ledbacklit display th generation intel core iu processor mb cache up to  ghz gb mhz ddr   each offer details            add to cart hour pick up price  instant savings   each astp